  "title": "Why the racial gap in life expectancy is declining in the United States",
  "abstract": "Our findings shed light on the sources of the declining racial gap in life expectancy in the United States, and help to identify where advances need to be made to achieve the goal of eliminating racial disparities in life expectancy.",
